Example Framework

The Extraction Index™

A score built from weighted categories:

Consumer Treatment

* shrinkflation
* deceptive packaging
* bait-and-switch pricing
* hidden fees
* subscription cancellation difficulty
* forced arbitration

Product Integrity

* repairability
* durability
* planned obsolescence
* proprietary lock-in
* anti-competitive accessories

Ownership Structure

* PE ownership
* roll-up acquisition behavior
* debt-loading after acquisition
* layoffs post-buyout

Labor Practices

* wage theft cases
* contractor abuse
* union-busting findings
* unsafe conditions

Transparency

* clear pricing
* sourcing visibility
* data collection clarity
* AI disclosure

Scam/Fraud Signals

* FTC actions
* class-action frequency
* regulatory fines
* repeat deceptive behavior

